{"tid":676120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【離奇爆竊案】男子潛入長安邨單位被制服 揭發為特遣隊警員","createTime":"2018-05-24T06:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:31:06.000Z","uid":19287,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6696e1e24eb9ff6971a764dbcc64775d59fb9a4d","tid":676120,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:20:56.000Z","msg":"【13:45】消息指，涉案男子為一名特遣隊警員，為該大廈住客，暫時未知他於案發時是否正在當值，重案組探員正調查他現身單位的原因<br />\n【10:25】葵青警區重案組接手調查<br />\n<br />\n早上7時半，青衣長安邨安湄樓發生爆竊案。男女住戶外出後因事折返，不料大門虛掩，赫見一名陌生男子大模施樣坐在客廳，懷疑他潛入爆竊，連忙將他截住及報警。警方在疑人身上沒有搜到可疑物品或屬於屋主的物件，現正在場調查，列爆竊案處理，疑人事後被警方帶走調查。"},{"pid":"526b9f00b7aef50760626f01bf93fdbe6de01e78","tid":676120,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"休班警 +1<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b598bec43c8c263191fb6aff2bc598be82bd4697","tid":676120,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會話見人冇閂門佢行入去幫人看屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec5261b9ef5cac438e8238700383983749fd6c7","tid":676120,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b53d1b9ed5151c1007ff65c289ef14edcc4a500f","tid":676120,"uid":45120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b598bec43c8c263191fb6aff2bc598be82bd4697","tid":676120,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會話見人冇閂門佢行入去幫人看屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"黑警包庇有咩講唔出"},{"pid":"6a93850534a8ca2d44dccc1bb59510cce7f816ec","tid":676120,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec5261b9ef5cac438e8238700383983749fd6c7","tid":676120,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"re